title: Beautiful Tudor Style East of Market Home on Huge Private Lot!
posting_body: ["You will fall in love with this charming 1930's meticulously maintained Tudor style home.", 'It sits on a huge .36 acre shaded fenced lot perfect for kids playing, gardening, or relaxing by the outdoor fire pit.', 'This yard boasts numerous mature fruit trees including plumbs, figs, pears, apples, grapes, walnuts, etc.', 'This neighborhood is quiet but neighbors are friendly and look out for one another.', "It's directly next to Kirkland Middle School and only a couple minutes from Peter Kirk Elementary, downtown Kirkland, and numerous parks.", 'This home has a ton of extra space including a huge basement that could be used as a workshop, office, or large storage area.', 'There are also a barn and large storage shed on the property.', 'Additionally you will enjoy the real wood burning fireplace to get through the winters, oversized premium washer/dryer, and professional yard maintenance included!', 'Available immediately!', 'Tenant responsible for utilities', '$4,500 Security Deposit', '$25 Application Fee', 'Sorry, no pets and no smokers', 'Rental Requirements:', '-Credit score 700 or above', '-Recurring verifiable monthly income of 2.5 times the rent', '-Positive reference from an established property management company', '-No evictions', 'Please call or text Vivian at', 'show contact info', 'for an application or to schedule a viewing.']
